Package com.o3dr.services.android.lib.gcs.link

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LinkConnectionStatus
    Conveys information about the link connection state.
    LinkEvent
    Stores all possible link events.
    LinkEventExtra
    Holds handles used to retrieve additional information broadcast along a link event.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    LinkConnectionStatus.FailureCode
    The possible failure codes that can be retrieved from the LinkConnectionStatus.getExtras() using key LinkConnectionStatus.EXTRA_ERROR_CODE.
    LinkConnectionStatus.StatusCode
    The possible status codes that notifies what state the link connection is in.
